INSTALL file for CrisoftRicette 1.0pre releases

*** COPYING FILES TO YOUR HARD DISK

Ungzip/unbzip and untar (or unzip for .zip version)
CrisoftRicette-1.0preX.tar.gz
CrisoftRicette-1.0preX.tar.bz2
CrisoftRicette-1.0preX.zip
into your web root folder.

*** SOFTWARE REQUIREMENTS

A web server (Apache is recommended)
MySQL ver. 3.23.XX or later
PHP 4.2.1 or later

PHP should be set up with
register_globals = off

*** CONFIGURING YOUR WEBSERVER

Correctly configure your httpd.conf file if needed (see Apache or your
webserver documentation).

*** CONFIGURING SOFTWARE

Edit config/foodie.inc.php with your database connection info.

If you wish to be able to email recipes, configure the email address too.


